        Community Title Schemes in Queensland: What Sellers of Apartments and Townhouses Need to Know
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        Queensland's community title framework is different from the strata system in other states. If you are selling an apartment or townhouse in Brisbane, understanding your disclosure obligations, by-laws, and what buyers will find in a body corporate records search will help your sale proceed without surprises.
      </p>
